e of this worldly life, in comparison to the Hereafter, but one of you dipping his finger in the sea? Let him see what he brings forth.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2858 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1089,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/05\/dua-zuhd-basic-needs\/","url_meta":{"origin":281,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Zuhd: The Prophet supplicates only for basic needs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 5, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, make provision for the family of Muhammad sufficiently nourishing.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6460, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1055 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Ibn Battal said, \"This narration is evidence for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3006,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/22\/jihad-in-way-of-allah-better-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":281,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Striving for Allah is better than the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA single endeavor or journey in the way of Allah is better than everything over which the sun rises and sets.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \u201cIt is better than the world and everything in it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23467,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/12\/world-needle-sea\/","url_meta":{"origin":281,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: World is nothing but a needle in the sea","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mustawrid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhat is the world compared to the Hereafter but like a needle dipped into ocean compared to its vast waters?\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 20\/308 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/12\/hereafter-concern-nur-qalb\/","url_meta":{"origin":281,"position":4},"title":"Ja&#8217;far on Akhirah: Worry about the Hereafter is light in the heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"J